<h3 id="basic-usage">Basic usage</h3>
<p>Call <code>ember-ted-select</code> in your template by providing a list of options and an action to trigger when the value of the select changes.</p>
<p>Remember, the selected value is not two-way bound. It's up to you to handle the new value within your action.</p>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6">
    {{code-snippet name="basic.hbs"}}
    {{code-snippet name="basic.js"}}
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-6">
    {{!-- BEGIN-SNIPPET basic  --}}
{{ted-select
  content=TEDevents
  onchange=(action "update")}}

Selected: {{selected.title}}
    {{!-- END-SNIPPET --}}
    <br>
  </div>
</div>
<br>

